description = "Huyan Zhuo, the Twin Rods. In the legend the imperial marshal sent to crush the outlaws, beaten by them, then won over by them. Here a decorated enforcement marshal who changed sides exactly once, the day he saw which side the cruelty was on. Disciplined and honorable, with two batons and no more illusions."
